section.section:
"Gift certificate" does not include:
A prepaid telephone calling card;
A prepaid technical support card;
A prepaid card for Internet services;
A coupon for discounted goods or services;
A gift certificate that is distributed to an individual under an awards, loyalty, or promotional program in which the recipient does not give money or value for the gift certificate; or
A gift card that:
Is processed through a national credit or debit card service; and
May be used to purchase goods or services from multiple unaffiliated sellers of goods or services.
